Source code deploys a chatbot using by Streamlit and AWS Bedrock Nova Micro FM

To run, download the 2 files into a common directory & run the following cmd. from the cmd. line:

streamlit run chatbot_frontend.py

Prerequisites:

Enable the FM in your Bedrock account (amazon.nova-micro-v1:0)
Ensure your uid that runs in VSCode Studio, has admin access to Bedrock